WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.977
Within this rapidly expanding and hyper-competitive environment, hyperscalers are no

00:00:03.977 --> 00:00:07.954
longer relying solely on direct infrastructure sales. Instead, cloud service

00:00:07.954 --> 00:00:11.930
providers are aggressively prioritizing and leveraging their strategic software partnerships

00:00:11.930 --> 00:00:15.907
to meet increasingly complex customer demands and profoundly accelerate their

00:00:15.907 --> 00:00:19.884
own ecosystem growth.
